1
00:00:00,440 --> 00:00:02,140
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:02,210 --> 00:00:03,410
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,480 --> 00:00:05,080
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:06,140 --> 00:00:07,550
Here comes the bride.

5
00:00:10,620 --> 00:00:11,750
(Episode 66)

6
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:14,470
Stop!

7
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,120
What's wrong with him?

8
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,390
What on earth?

9
00:02:32,660 --> 00:02:33,660
What's going on?

10
00:02:34,160 --> 00:02:35,630
What is he doing?

11
00:02:36,690 --> 00:02:37,700
What?

12
00:02:37,700 --> 00:02:38,700
No.

13
00:02:38,930 --> 00:02:41,570
This wedding can't happen.

14
00:02:42,270 --> 00:02:44,070
Did his memories come back?

15
00:02:45,100 --> 00:02:46,100
You...

16
00:02:47,640 --> 00:02:48,640
Don't tell me...

17
00:02:49,370 --> 00:02:52,040
Did he get his memory back?

18
00:02:53,140 --> 00:02:56,380
What the heck
does he think he's doing?

19
00:02:59,020 --> 00:03:02,020
Wait.
Could his memories have come back?

20
00:03:04,390 --> 00:03:05,390
Min Jun.

21
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:09,030
How could you marry her
when you knew everything?

22
00:03:09,830 --> 00:03:14,130
You're selfish to the very end.

23
00:03:14,430 --> 00:03:17,040
- You coward!
- Hyun Jun!

24
00:03:17,100 --> 00:03:18,100
Min Jun.

25
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:29,680
What is all this?

26
00:03:31,350 --> 00:03:34,250
Min Jun...
His memories must be back.

27
00:03:57,110 --> 00:04:00,980
Get out of my way.
I'm going back to the wedding.

28
00:04:02,880 --> 00:04:07,050
No. This wedding is a mistake.

29
00:04:07,450 --> 00:04:10,120
You're only making this choice
because you lost your memory.

30
00:04:10,590 --> 00:04:11,860
Look at me!

31
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:14,390
Please.

32
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:17,000
Try to remember me, Jin Ju.

33
00:04:20,570 --> 00:04:21,630
I...

34
00:04:22,630 --> 00:04:24,640
don't know
what you're talking about.

35
00:04:25,100 --> 00:04:26,370
Baek Jin Ju.

36
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:29,440
I'm leaving. Get out of my way.

37
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:31,210
Just once!

38
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:35,850
Try to remember
how much we loved each other.

39
00:04:36,510 --> 00:04:41,420
How much we longed for each other,
and the long road we took...

40
00:04:42,450 --> 00:04:44,220
to find our way back to one another.

41
00:04:45,390 --> 00:04:46,460
Please.

42
00:05:02,270 --> 00:05:04,140
I think Min Jun
regained his memories.

43
00:05:04,410 --> 00:05:05,510
What do I do?

44
00:05:05,510 --> 00:05:07,650
I need to see Min Jun first.

45
00:05:09,010 --> 00:05:10,420
You're going to take my side, right?

46
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:13,620
I was just doing what you told me.
You'll back me up, won't you?

47
00:05:16,050 --> 00:05:18,420
- We'll talk about this later.
- Mother!

48
00:05:18,760 --> 00:05:19,990
Kim Myung Hui.

49
00:05:19,990 --> 00:05:22,660
You just had to ruin his wedding,
didn't you?

50
00:05:22,660 --> 00:05:24,260
Is this your idea of revenge?

51
00:05:30,270 --> 00:05:31,470
Revenge?

52
00:05:39,140 --> 00:05:41,480
Hyun Jun, wait. Hyun Jun!

53
00:05:47,290 --> 00:05:48,320
Don't do this.

54
00:05:49,950 --> 00:05:50,990
I...

55
00:05:52,490 --> 00:05:54,560
can't ruin this wedding.

56
00:06:01,100 --> 00:06:02,400
Jin Ju, please.

57
00:06:03,770 --> 00:06:05,370
Chloe!

58
00:06:09,440 --> 00:06:10,610
Don't!

59
00:06:16,750 --> 00:06:19,080
You're really going
to see it through?

60
00:06:20,050 --> 00:06:22,450
You tricked Jin Ju
into this marriage...

61
00:06:22,450 --> 00:06:24,420
while both of us had amnesia.

62
00:06:25,420 --> 00:06:26,760
Don't you feel guilty at all?

63
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:29,460
- Have you no shame?
- No.

64
00:06:30,030 --> 00:06:32,900
I don't care what you say.
I have no regrets.

65
00:06:34,470 --> 00:06:35,870
This wedding...

66
00:06:36,230 --> 00:06:38,700
was a choice we made together,
without you.

67
00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:41,240
The two of you?

68
00:06:49,280 --> 00:06:50,820
It's always been Jin Ju and me.

69
00:06:51,380 --> 00:06:53,520
You're the one who came between us.

70
00:06:54,350 --> 00:06:56,950
So how can you say
the choice was mutual?

71
00:06:57,590 --> 00:06:58,690
Stop!

72
00:07:02,960 --> 00:07:04,100
Just stop it.

73
00:07:05,960 --> 00:07:10,070
Hyun Jun's right.
We both chose to get married.

74
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:16,710
Baek Jin Ju.

75
00:07:18,310 --> 00:07:22,010
That's right.
I never lost my memory,

76
00:07:22,410 --> 00:07:25,380
and Hyun Jun didn't trick me
into marrying him.

77
00:07:26,550 --> 00:07:30,560
In fact, I'm the one
who asked him to marry me.

78
00:07:31,220 --> 00:07:34,590
To become part of the Adele family
and get my revenge,

79
00:07:34,660 --> 00:07:36,290
I begged him to help me.

80
00:07:38,100 --> 00:07:41,700
This is the marriage I chose,
so please...

81
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:43,270
stop this.

82
00:07:46,140 --> 00:07:48,470
Was this really your choice?

83
00:07:57,280 --> 00:08:01,350
How could you leave me
and marry Hyun Jun?

84
00:08:02,850 --> 00:08:03,860
You know,

85
00:08:04,790 --> 00:08:06,690
the moment I heard your name,

86
00:08:06,990 --> 00:08:08,360
I remembered you.

87
00:08:09,790 --> 00:08:11,230
You're engraved...

88
00:08:11,830 --> 00:08:13,970
right here in my heart.

89
00:08:13,970 --> 00:08:15,100
You're...

90
00:08:16,330 --> 00:08:18,500
no help to my revenge.

91
00:08:19,500 --> 00:08:20,500
What?

92
00:08:21,910 --> 00:08:25,080
You were against my revenge
from the start.

93
00:08:25,140 --> 00:08:27,010
That was because
it was too dangerous.

94
00:08:27,080 --> 00:08:28,610
I wanted us to find another way.

95
00:08:28,610 --> 00:08:30,010
This marriage...

96
00:08:31,820 --> 00:08:33,580
is the other solution I found.

97
00:08:44,260 --> 00:08:48,270
I know everything
our father did now.

98
00:08:48,700 --> 00:08:51,340
You're not the only one
who can help Jin Ju.

99
00:08:52,270 --> 00:08:53,740
From now on,

100
00:08:54,810 --> 00:08:57,540
I'll be the one to do
whatever it takes for her,

101
00:08:58,810 --> 00:09:00,080
so stay out of it.

102
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:33,180
Are you that worried about Min Jun?

103
00:09:35,110 --> 00:09:36,380
Min Jun...

104
00:09:38,880 --> 00:09:41,020
almost died because of me.

105
00:09:44,090 --> 00:09:45,360
That's why...

106
00:09:46,190 --> 00:09:48,430
I didn't want him
to get hurt anymore.

107
00:09:49,790 --> 00:09:52,230
I just wanted him
to never regain his memories...

108
00:09:53,230 --> 00:09:55,470
and stay oblivious to everything.

109
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:00,040
So?

110
00:10:02,410 --> 00:10:04,310
Do you want to go back to him?

111
00:10:08,310 --> 00:10:09,980
You know...

112
00:10:10,680 --> 00:10:11,850
I can't do that.

113
00:10:14,590 --> 00:10:15,590
It's just...

114
00:10:16,490 --> 00:10:18,090
I feel like I've hurt Min Jun...

115
00:10:19,720 --> 00:10:21,530
all over again.

116
00:10:23,460 --> 00:10:24,500
That's why.

117
00:10:25,430 --> 00:10:26,600
Anyway,

118
00:10:27,530 --> 00:10:29,370
you're not going back to him, right?

119
00:10:33,340 --> 00:10:34,610
That's all I needed to hear.

120
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:42,910
Chloe, goodness. Hey.

121
00:10:43,110 --> 00:10:44,550
Where were you?

122
00:10:44,850 --> 00:10:46,950
I looked outside,
thinking you had left.

123
00:10:47,420 --> 00:10:48,420
Are you okay?

124
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:50,320
Yes.

125
00:10:50,690 --> 00:10:53,260
- I'm fine.
- Let's talk later.

126
00:10:53,260 --> 00:10:55,730
First, we need to get on
with the ceremony.

127
00:10:55,790 --> 00:10:58,600
Right. Let's go in. Come on.

128
00:11:05,500 --> 00:11:06,500
Min Jun.

129
00:11:11,210 --> 00:11:12,210
Min Jun.

130
00:11:14,680 --> 00:11:15,950
What happened?

131
00:11:22,990 --> 00:11:24,020
Why...

132
00:11:25,090 --> 00:11:26,720
didn't you tell me?

133
00:11:27,760 --> 00:11:28,860
So it's true.

134
00:11:30,260 --> 00:11:32,060
Your memories are back.

135
00:11:32,730 --> 00:11:34,270
You should've helped me...

136
00:11:35,170 --> 00:11:37,470
regain my memories sooner.

137
00:11:39,300 --> 00:11:41,970
Just why did you hide
the truth from me?

138
00:11:47,140 --> 00:11:49,550
You almost died
because of Oh Jung Ran.

139
00:11:51,980 --> 00:11:54,520
I dragged you into
my fight with her,

140
00:11:55,220 --> 00:11:57,120
and that's why you got run over.

141
00:11:58,420 --> 00:12:00,720
Watching you fight for your life,

142
00:12:01,830 --> 00:12:05,530
I can't tell you
how much I blamed myself.

143
00:12:08,230 --> 00:12:10,030
When you lost your memories,

144
00:12:11,870 --> 00:12:13,800
I only had one thought.

145
00:12:14,670 --> 00:12:15,770
I didn't...

146
00:12:16,570 --> 00:12:18,040
want you to get hurt...

147
00:12:18,980 --> 00:12:20,780
or suffer anymore.

148
00:12:22,780 --> 00:12:25,480
I thought if you didn't remember
the painful things...

149
00:12:26,120 --> 00:12:27,850
and kept your distance from Chloe,

150
00:12:32,390 --> 00:12:34,790
it would bring you peace.

151
00:12:40,500 --> 00:12:43,170
No. It wasn't for my sake.

152
00:12:43,730 --> 00:12:46,240
You just chose the path
that was more convenient for you.

153
00:12:47,170 --> 00:12:49,270
If you had really cared about me,

154
00:12:49,340 --> 00:12:53,080
you would've helped me
get my memories back sooner.

155
00:12:53,210 --> 00:12:56,210
You should've given me a chance
to stop the woman I love...

156
00:12:56,210 --> 00:12:58,150
from getting married.

157
00:12:58,550 --> 00:13:01,120
While I was completely in the dark
and couldn't do anything,

158
00:13:01,190 --> 00:13:02,990
this is what happened.

159
00:13:09,730 --> 00:13:12,400
So don't tell me you did it for me.

160
00:13:26,940 --> 00:13:28,080
Min Jun.

161
00:13:34,390 --> 00:13:35,650
Min Jun.

162
00:13:48,370 --> 00:13:52,440
They're here. They're back.
The bride and groom are back!

163
00:13:52,740 --> 00:13:56,870
Let's start over. Hurry up.
Lock that door.

164
00:13:58,580 --> 00:14:00,010
Sit down, people.

165
00:14:13,020 --> 00:14:14,190
Remember what I said?

166
00:14:15,230 --> 00:14:16,690
Once the ceremony begins,

167
00:14:18,330 --> 00:14:20,060
I won't look back.

168
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:23,570
Unless you're going to stop now,

169
00:14:25,140 --> 00:14:26,400
just follow my lead.

170
00:14:32,140 --> 00:14:33,280
No.

171
00:14:34,810 --> 00:14:35,810
You'll...

172
00:14:36,080 --> 00:14:37,650
be following my lead.

173
00:14:56,100 --> 00:14:57,230
Min Jun.

174
00:14:58,100 --> 00:15:02,570
As I walk down this aisle,
I'm going to forget everything.

175
00:15:11,280 --> 00:15:13,650
The moments we loved each other.

176
00:15:27,430 --> 00:15:30,070
The moments
we longed for each other.

177
00:15:30,470 --> 00:15:31,700
All of it.

178
00:15:37,780 --> 00:15:41,680
I don't want you to be
in danger again because of me.

179
00:15:45,780 --> 00:15:49,150
I don't want my feelings for you
to make me give up everything...

180
00:15:49,390 --> 00:15:51,120
I've worked for.

181
00:15:52,760 --> 00:15:54,430
I've made my choice,

182
00:15:54,930 --> 00:15:56,960
and there's no going back.

183
00:16:04,100 --> 00:16:05,140
No.

184
00:16:06,200 --> 00:16:08,440
No!

185
00:16:08,440 --> 00:16:09,470
Min Jun!

186
00:16:10,070 --> 00:16:12,810
Stop it. It's too late.

187
00:16:14,550 --> 00:16:17,510
No. I can't lose her like this.

188
00:16:18,920 --> 00:16:20,780
This is the marriage Chloe chose.

189
00:16:30,030 --> 00:16:32,930
Both before and after
she lost her memory,

190
00:16:34,100 --> 00:16:36,170
Chloe wanted this wedding.

191
00:16:37,500 --> 00:16:39,900
You can't make her walk away.

192
00:17:41,670 --> 00:17:43,430
Kim Myung Hui, Park Min Jun.

193
00:17:44,640 --> 00:17:47,070
How dare they try to ruin
my Hyun Jun's wedding?

194
00:17:47,670 --> 00:17:50,270
Just wait
until the ceremony is over.

195
00:17:50,340 --> 00:17:51,680
I'll make them pay.

196
00:17:58,450 --> 00:18:00,620
We've dealt with
Oh Jung Ran's people.

197
00:18:00,620 --> 00:18:03,220
All that's left is for Chairman Park
to wake up. Why hasn't he yet?

198
00:18:03,750 --> 00:18:05,390
Doctor,

199
00:18:06,520 --> 00:18:08,760
are you sure the chairman
is going to wake up?

200
00:18:09,930 --> 00:18:12,130
There were no issues
with the treatment.

201
00:18:12,130 --> 00:18:13,400
We just have to wait and see.

202
00:18:13,630 --> 00:18:16,800
Min Jun stormed out of here earlier.

203
00:18:17,230 --> 00:18:19,200
Shouldn't we call him
and see what's wrong?

204
00:18:19,270 --> 00:18:20,340
You're right.

205
00:18:20,770 --> 00:18:21,970
I was so busy dealing
with everything...

206
00:18:22,040 --> 00:18:23,040
that I completely forgot.

207
00:18:23,810 --> 00:18:25,110
Let's head out and call him.

208
00:18:42,830 --> 00:18:46,100
How's the chairman?
Is he really going to wake up?

209
00:18:46,160 --> 00:18:48,500
The person you've called
is not available.

210
00:18:51,600 --> 00:18:54,340
Is something going on?
He's not answering.

211
00:18:54,400 --> 00:18:58,040
- At least send him a text.
- Sure.

212
00:19:04,550 --> 00:19:05,750
That guy is waking up.

213
00:19:17,160 --> 00:19:18,500
Am I dreaming?

214
00:19:18,600 --> 00:19:23,870
I guess guarding the master bedroom
has been taking a toll on me.

215
00:19:25,040 --> 00:19:26,700
Too bad for you.

216
00:19:27,470 --> 00:19:29,010
This isn't a dream.

217
00:19:29,940 --> 00:19:31,580
This is all very real.

218
00:19:33,040 --> 00:19:36,110
What? What the...

219
00:19:36,510 --> 00:19:39,050
What in the world is going on?

220
00:19:39,820 --> 00:19:43,320
Where's Jung Ran?
What about our Hyun Jun?

221
00:19:47,320 --> 00:19:50,990
This can't be happening. No!

222
00:19:52,300 --> 00:19:53,460
Ms. Kim.

223
00:19:53,630 --> 00:19:55,330
Ms. Kim!

224
00:19:55,500 --> 00:19:56,700
Welcome home, Ms. Kim.

225
00:19:56,700 --> 00:19:59,500
I hope the wedding and reception
are both going smoothly.

226
00:19:59,570 --> 00:20:02,040
Fortunately,
the wedding is still going on.

227
00:20:02,110 --> 00:20:05,310
At least that gives the chairman
some time to recover.

228
00:20:05,380 --> 00:20:06,380
But...

229
00:20:08,350 --> 00:20:11,420
It's about Director Park Min Jun.

230
00:20:11,850 --> 00:20:14,050
He suddenly ran out,
and we can't reach him.

231
00:20:14,690 --> 00:20:16,520
We'll talk about that later.

232
00:20:17,550 --> 00:20:18,920
- Ms. Kim.
- Sure.

233
00:20:19,160 --> 00:20:21,120
You can't do this.

234
00:20:21,790 --> 00:20:25,130
You said you'd divide Adele equally
with Jung Ran.

235
00:20:25,130 --> 00:20:27,000
How could you betray her like this?

236
00:20:27,360 --> 00:20:28,900
This isn't right.

237
00:20:29,930 --> 00:20:31,740
If Chairman Park wakes up,

238
00:20:32,170 --> 00:20:36,370
where does that leave Jung Ran
and Hyun Jun?

239
00:20:36,440 --> 00:20:39,640
Ms. Kim, will Chairman Park
even wake up?

240
00:20:40,110 --> 00:20:42,510
If he does,
I'll return to his side immediately.

241
00:20:43,110 --> 00:20:44,780
What am I hearing?

242
00:20:44,780 --> 00:20:47,380
Manager Kang,
you can't just switch sides.

243
00:20:47,450 --> 00:20:49,290
You joined us,
so you have to see it through!

244
00:20:49,390 --> 00:20:50,890
From the very beginning,

245
00:20:51,720 --> 00:20:53,220
I was being blackmailed.

246
00:20:53,620 --> 00:20:56,090
Didn't I already say
I'd return to my post...

247
00:20:56,160 --> 00:20:57,490
if the chairman woke up?

248
00:20:57,560 --> 00:21:01,670
So you've been planning
to double-cross us from the start?

249
00:21:01,670 --> 00:21:04,370
You can explain yourselves later.

250
00:21:06,940 --> 00:21:11,440
Ms. Kim! You can't do this.
If Chairman Park wakes up,

251
00:21:11,510 --> 00:21:13,780
Jung Ran's dead!

252
00:21:14,110 --> 00:21:17,610
Ms. Kim, please don't.

253
00:21:20,020 --> 00:21:22,690
Ms. Kim!

254
00:21:25,390 --> 00:21:27,720
I've done everything I can
to treat him.

255
00:21:27,790 --> 00:21:29,930
And he's still unconscious?

256
00:21:29,930 --> 00:21:31,530
That's what I find strange.

257
00:21:31,530 --> 00:21:34,500
He should've woken up by now.

258
00:21:34,560 --> 00:21:36,270
Were we too late?

259
00:21:36,470 --> 00:21:39,440
Perhaps it's time to move
the chairman to a hospital.

260
00:21:41,140 --> 00:21:43,640
Oh Jung Ran will be back
once the wedding is over.

261
00:21:43,640 --> 00:21:44,840
We need to be ready.

262
00:21:51,780 --> 00:21:54,420
I know it wasn't easy today, Ms. Oh.

263
00:21:54,520 --> 00:21:58,190
Are weddings always this exhausting?

264
00:21:58,320 --> 00:22:01,390
That's all because of the trouble
Director Park Min Jun caused.

265
00:22:02,730 --> 00:22:05,230
It's because that punk
got his memories back.

266
00:22:05,830 --> 00:22:09,170
But does that give him the right to storm
into someone else's wedding?

267
00:22:09,730 --> 00:22:12,570
Just how crazy is he about Chloe?

268
00:22:13,970 --> 00:22:15,310
Seriously?

269
00:22:21,210 --> 00:22:22,210
You.

270
00:22:23,850 --> 00:22:26,320
You, explain yourself.

271
00:22:26,650 --> 00:22:28,990
What did you say when Park Min Jun
dragged you out of here?

272
00:22:29,550 --> 00:22:32,090
Just how serious are you
with that punk...

273
00:22:32,090 --> 00:22:33,790
to cause this kind of scene?

274
00:22:34,360 --> 00:22:36,690
What are you talking about?

275
00:22:36,990 --> 00:22:39,800
Why are you taking it out on her
when he was the one who went crazy?

276
00:22:40,400 --> 00:22:42,930
It takes two to tango.

277
00:22:43,270 --> 00:22:45,370
Would he have crashed the wedding
if there was nothing between you?

278
00:22:45,540 --> 00:22:46,870
For crying out loud.

279
00:22:47,270 --> 00:22:48,370
I've heard enough.

280
00:22:48,570 --> 00:22:50,570
Are you insulting Chloe right now?

281
00:22:50,670 --> 00:22:53,210
Why are you two so defensive?

282
00:22:53,540 --> 00:22:55,680
Can't I even ask what happened?

283
00:22:57,610 --> 00:22:59,120
Everyone, stop.

284
00:23:00,320 --> 00:23:01,320
Mother,

285
00:23:01,820 --> 00:23:03,750
since I lost my memory,

286
00:23:03,750 --> 00:23:06,320
I don't know
what kind of relationship...

287
00:23:06,320 --> 00:23:07,490
Director Park and I had.

288
00:23:08,230 --> 00:23:11,630
But right now, Hyun Jun
is the only one in my heart.

289
00:23:12,430 --> 00:23:15,030
That's right.
Chloe's done nothing wrong.

290
00:23:15,430 --> 00:23:17,500
Min Jun was infatuated with her,
and then his memory...

291
00:23:19,900 --> 00:23:22,010
He just went crazy
and acted out on his own,

292
00:23:23,240 --> 00:23:24,270
so drop it.

293
00:23:26,480 --> 00:23:30,480
In any case, I'm truly sorry
for causing such a scene.

294
00:23:47,130 --> 00:23:50,000
Hyun Jun didn't trick me
into marrying him.

295
00:23:50,670 --> 00:23:54,300
In fact, I'm the one
who asked him to marry me.

296
00:23:54,740 --> 00:23:56,640
This is the marriage I chose,

297
00:23:58,510 --> 00:24:01,750
so please stop this.

298
00:24:01,880 --> 00:24:03,010
You're...

299
00:24:04,180 --> 00:24:06,350
no help to my revenge.

300
00:24:06,550 --> 00:24:07,850
This marriage...

301
00:24:09,720 --> 00:24:11,490
is the other solution I found.

302
00:24:14,360 --> 00:24:15,360
Revenge?

303
00:24:16,330 --> 00:24:20,030
She's marrying Hyun Jun
to get her revenge?

304
00:24:21,900 --> 00:24:23,070
But why Hyun Jun?

305
00:24:24,330 --> 00:24:26,240
What could her plan be?

306
00:24:31,440 --> 00:24:33,510
If Father wakes up,

307
00:24:34,640 --> 00:24:36,180
what happens then?

308
00:24:46,560 --> 00:24:49,060
- This is quality tea.
- Oh my, Yu Na's here.

309
00:24:49,130 --> 00:24:51,090
- Is that Yu Na?
- Hey, Yu Na.

310
00:24:52,100 --> 00:24:53,600
Goodness. Yu Na.

311
00:24:54,330 --> 00:24:55,400
What?

312
00:24:55,930 --> 00:24:57,770
Did something happen at the wedding?

313
00:24:58,030 --> 00:24:59,800
Tell me about it.

314
00:25:00,270 --> 00:25:03,040
You should be home beaming
after catching the bouquet,

315
00:25:03,410 --> 00:25:05,540
but here you are,
wearing a deep frown.

316
00:25:05,880 --> 00:25:06,880
Mom.

317
00:25:07,180 --> 00:25:08,780
- Yes?
- Dad.

318
00:25:09,280 --> 00:25:11,150
- What is it?
- What do I do now?

319
00:25:11,210 --> 00:25:12,820
- What?
- What?

320
00:25:12,880 --> 00:25:14,120
What do you mean?

321
00:25:15,320 --> 00:25:17,420
Min Jun got all his memories back.

322
00:25:18,220 --> 00:25:20,160
- What?
- Are you serious?

323
00:25:21,120 --> 00:25:22,530
- Yes.
- Oh, dear.

324
00:25:22,530 --> 00:25:24,260
He remembers everything.

325
00:25:25,060 --> 00:25:28,270
Oh, dear. What are we going to do?

326
00:25:29,100 --> 00:25:30,800
But still,

327
00:25:31,530 --> 00:25:35,110
you've been so devoted to him
all this time.

328
00:25:35,770 --> 00:25:38,610
If that devotion has grown
into real affection,

329
00:25:39,140 --> 00:25:40,240
won't things be okay?

330
00:25:40,580 --> 00:25:41,580
No.

331
00:25:42,850 --> 00:25:44,410
The way he looked at me...

332
00:25:45,080 --> 00:25:46,220
was terrifying.

333
00:25:47,520 --> 00:25:50,190
I think he hates me more now
than before he lost his memory.

334
00:25:52,120 --> 00:25:54,220
Is it because I was pretending
to be Baek Jin Ju?

335
00:25:54,490 --> 00:25:56,790
He must think I deceived him.

336
00:25:57,460 --> 00:25:59,230
What if he never wants
to see me again?

337
00:25:59,730 --> 00:26:02,070
- Yu Na.
- What are we going to do?

338
00:26:02,900 --> 00:26:06,470
If only you were pregnant,
things would be fine.

339
00:26:06,700 --> 00:26:09,310
Is a baby all you can think about
right now?

340
00:26:09,370 --> 00:26:10,370
Unbelievable.

341
00:26:11,110 --> 00:26:13,110
Yu Na,
since things have come to this,

342
00:26:13,840 --> 00:26:15,580
maybe you should just give up...

343
00:26:15,580 --> 00:26:16,680
No.

344
00:26:17,550 --> 00:26:18,820
I can't end it like this.

345
00:26:19,920 --> 00:26:21,550
Not after coming this far.

346
00:26:23,220 --> 00:26:25,090
I have to win Min Jun back,
no matter what.

347
00:26:27,690 --> 00:26:30,630
He smiled at me...

348
00:26:31,430 --> 00:26:32,800
and held me.

349
00:26:36,400 --> 00:26:38,070
There's no way
I'm letting it end like this.

350
00:26:44,340 --> 00:26:45,410
For crying out loud.

351
00:26:50,750 --> 00:26:53,180
So this is where
you've been staying.

352
00:26:54,820 --> 00:26:55,890
Have a seat.

353
00:26:55,950 --> 00:26:58,760
We have a lot to discuss
about what to do next.

354
00:26:59,120 --> 00:27:00,420
Right, of course.

355
00:27:08,900 --> 00:27:11,330
Who knew a wedding
could be this difficult?

356
00:27:12,140 --> 00:27:15,570
Of all days for Park Min Jun
to get his memory back.

357
00:27:16,410 --> 00:27:18,310
But at least we got through it.

358
00:27:18,310 --> 00:27:20,180
I'm worried about what comes next.

359
00:27:20,680 --> 00:27:23,450
Park Min Jun isn't one
to give up easily,

360
00:27:24,110 --> 00:27:26,720
and I doubt he'll just stand by
and accept this marriage.

361
00:27:27,020 --> 00:27:28,050
I'll stop him.

362
00:27:28,620 --> 00:27:30,220
Whatever Min Jun does,

363
00:27:30,920 --> 00:27:32,360
I will absolutely
protect this marriage.

364
00:27:32,560 --> 00:27:34,520
I'm not going to give up either.

365
00:27:35,830 --> 00:27:38,130
Okay, fine.

366
00:27:39,060 --> 00:27:40,060
That aside,

367
00:27:41,400 --> 00:27:44,270
what are you going to do
about the logistics?

368
00:27:45,340 --> 00:27:47,570
For starters, what's your excuse
for the honeymoon?

369
00:27:47,840 --> 00:27:50,070
Hyun Jun's family thinks
you're staying at a hotel tonight...

370
00:27:50,140 --> 00:27:51,310
and leaving tomorrow morning.

371
00:27:52,210 --> 00:27:54,580
We're going to follow through
with that.

372
00:27:54,980 --> 00:27:56,050
What?

373
00:27:56,910 --> 00:28:00,350
What I meant, Father,
is that I'll be going alone.

374
00:28:00,780 --> 00:28:02,290
It's not like I can sleep here.

375
00:28:04,790 --> 00:28:06,090
As for the honeymoon,

376
00:28:06,090 --> 00:28:09,090
I'll make an excuse
that I suddenly felt sick.

377
00:28:10,360 --> 00:28:14,000
- No. I'll say I'm sick.
- Of course you should.

378
00:28:14,330 --> 00:28:18,500
Your mother is just looking
for any excuse to pick on Jin Ju.

379
00:28:19,700 --> 00:28:20,770
I'm sorry about that.

380
00:28:22,640 --> 00:28:25,080
And what about living together?

381
00:28:25,340 --> 00:28:27,510
You'll have to get ready
to move into his house right away.

382
00:28:28,240 --> 00:28:30,150
My goodness, to fool the family,

383
00:28:31,310 --> 00:28:32,650
you two will have to share a room.

384
00:28:34,050 --> 00:28:35,920
Unbelievable.

385
00:28:36,290 --> 00:28:37,290
Don't worry.

386
00:28:38,120 --> 00:28:39,560
I'll never do anything...

387
00:28:40,490 --> 00:28:41,620
that Jin Ju doesn't want.

388
00:28:57,310 --> 00:28:58,310
Yes, what is it?

389
00:29:00,040 --> 00:29:01,950
A report from the intel team?
That's unexpected.

390
00:29:02,680 --> 00:29:03,680
What's going on?

391
00:29:06,720 --> 00:29:08,590
Something happened
with the Adele family?

392
00:29:09,490 --> 00:29:10,490
What are you talking about?

393
00:29:15,660 --> 00:29:18,230
Hold on. Why are all the lights off?

394
00:29:18,930 --> 00:29:19,930
Manager Kang.

395
00:29:20,460 --> 00:29:21,460
Geun Tae!

396
00:29:27,270 --> 00:29:28,940
What are you saying?

397
00:29:33,110 --> 00:29:34,940
Kim Myung Hui, why you...

398
00:29:36,450 --> 00:29:38,950
Don't tell me
you snuck Park Tae Ho out.

399
00:29:40,080 --> 00:29:41,180
Where is he?

400
00:30:07,180 --> 00:30:09,180
How...

401
00:30:10,450 --> 00:30:12,120
How did you wake him up?

402
00:30:18,990 --> 00:30:21,090
Oh Jung Ran will be back
once the wedding is over.

403
00:30:21,160 --> 00:30:22,260
We need to be ready.

404
00:30:23,660 --> 00:30:25,260
His treatment has been completed,

405
00:30:25,830 --> 00:30:27,730
so there's no point in moving him
to a hospital.

406
00:30:29,630 --> 00:30:31,200
We just have to hold on...

407
00:30:31,200 --> 00:30:33,070
and wait for the chairman
to wake up.

408
00:30:33,300 --> 00:30:34,870
What if he doesn't wake up?

409
00:30:36,070 --> 00:30:37,570
When Oh Jung Ran gets back,

410
00:30:37,840 --> 00:30:39,340
she'll be outraged
that you deceived her...

411
00:30:39,340 --> 00:30:40,680
and stabbed her in the back.

412
00:30:40,980 --> 00:30:45,480
What if she tries to harm you
and Director Park Min Jun?

413
00:30:46,280 --> 00:30:48,690
That should never happen.

414
00:30:57,390 --> 00:30:58,930
Sir!

415
00:31:01,400 --> 00:31:02,430
Are you awake?

416
00:31:03,470 --> 00:31:04,470
Sir.

417
00:31:06,400 --> 00:31:09,210
The chairman is awake.

418
00:31:12,240 --> 00:31:13,280
Oh Jung Ran.

419
00:31:14,110 --> 00:31:15,910
How dare you render me helpless...

420
00:31:16,550 --> 00:31:18,380
and try to tear Adele in two?

421
00:31:19,050 --> 00:31:21,080
You dared to take my place...

422
00:31:22,450 --> 00:31:24,420
and seize control of Adele?

423
00:31:26,660 --> 00:31:30,690
Run! I said, run!

424
00:31:36,100 --> 00:31:37,970
No, let me go.

425
00:31:37,970 --> 00:31:39,840
Let go of me!

426
00:31:40,200 --> 00:31:41,200
Let me go!

427
00:31:42,340 --> 00:31:43,340
Mom!

428
00:31:48,240 --> 00:31:49,250
Father.

429
00:31:49,710 --> 00:31:50,710
Sir.

430
00:31:54,450 --> 00:31:55,520
Sir,

431
00:31:56,690 --> 00:31:57,690
there's...

432
00:31:58,420 --> 00:32:00,890
something I haven't told you yet.

433
00:32:01,560 --> 00:32:02,960
It's about Hyun Jun.

434
00:32:05,090 --> 00:32:06,100
You...

435
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:10,470
What are you about to say?

436
00:32:53,510 --> 00:32:56,410
(Pearl in Red)

437
00:32:56,880 --> 00:33:00,050
Don't get too comfortable.
You think Kim Myung Hui saved you?

438
00:33:00,150 --> 00:33:01,150
- Let go.
- No.

439
00:33:01,180 --> 00:33:03,390
Believe me when I say
she'll betray you.

440
00:33:03,420 --> 00:33:06,760
How dare you
put me out of commission...

441
00:33:06,760 --> 00:33:08,320
and then yell at me?

442
00:33:08,760 --> 00:33:11,530
- Our marriage still stands, right?
- Min Jun.

443
00:33:11,760 --> 00:33:13,060
You're not going
to end our marriage...

444
00:33:13,060 --> 00:33:15,630
because I didn't become chairman,
are you?

445
00:33:17,000 --> 00:33:19,000
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
